             navigation stack to execute successfully. The plan is designed to move the robot to a specific position and orientation. If any part of the plan fails, it 
             will be retried until it succeeds. The navigation stack's RecoveryNodeOrigiin and RecoveryNodeGoal are set to handle retries and recovery actions. The overall 
